      "duration": "",
      "published_date": "",
      "apple_rating": 0,
      "chunk_text": "對你跟別人的關係而言也會是一種破壞如果對於這個量表有興趣的話",
      "embedding": [],
      "language": "zh",
      "created_at": "2025-07-10T14:38:21.044749",
